Dear Dr Mad Mushroom,
The Az 1 TeamCoord at Org A set up your account on Patients Know Best so that you can help your patients online.

To get started, you need to complete your registration on the Patients Know Best website, so please click on this link:

http://pkb-frontend-1/clinicianRegistrationUserForm.action?icode=team_az&uid=2145&temp=uG3vITKNBU

After that, you can use Patients Know Best to work. Welcome to our site; we hope you like it!

Please do not reply to this email; this address is not monitored. Click this link to log into your record.

Yours,

Patients Know Best Help Team

Dear Dr Mad Mushroom,
The Az 1 TeamCoord is setting up Team AZ accounts on Patients Know Best so that you can work with Org A patients online.

You will need to transfer your existing account to Org A, so please click on the following link and follow the instructions:

http://pkb-frontend-1/patient/becomeInstituteClinician.action?icode=team_az&uid=2145&invitationId=32f438c4-88dc-4041-a78d-8c920481f145&e=madmushroom%40pkbtest.com

Please do not reply to this email; this address is not monitored. Click this link to log into your record.

Yours,

Patients Know Best Help Team
